---
---

<section class="thesis-masked" id="thesis">
  <div class="thesis-grid">
    <div class="thesis-visual">
      <div class="thesis-photo"></div>
      <svg class="thesis-svg" viewBox="0 0 700 640" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="thesisCandleGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E8112D"></stop>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7A0E1C"></stop>
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <g stroke="#E8112D" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3">
          <line x1="80" y1="130" x2="180" y2="95"></line>
          <line x1="180" y1="95" x2="260" y2="160"></line>
          <line x1="80" y1="130" x2="150" y2="215"></line>
          <line x1="150" y1="215" x2="260" y2="160"></line>
          <line x1="150" y1="215" x2="110" y2="300"></line>
          <line x1="260" y1="160" x2="290" y2="270"></line>
          <line x1="110" y1="300" x2="290" y2="270"></line>
        </g>
        <g fill="#E8112D">
          <circle cx="80" cy="130" r="5"></circle>
          <circle cx="180" cy="95" r="4"></circle>
          <circle cx="260" cy="160" r="6"></circle>
          <circle cx="150" cy="215" r="4"></circle>
          <circle cx="110" cy="300" r="5"></circle>
          <circle cx="290" cy="270" r="4"></circle>
        </g>
        <text x="60" y="470" font-family="Archivo Expanded, sans-serif" font-weight="800" font-size="220" fill="none" stroke="#E8112D" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.24">%</text>
        <text x="500" y="90" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="28" fill="#E8112D" opacity="0.26">$</text>
        <text x="560" y="560" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="24" fill="#E8112D" opacity="0.2">Rp</text>
        <text x="120" y="60" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="20" fill="#E8112D" opacity="0.2">S$</text>
        <g transform="translate(60,420)">
          <line x1="10" y1="30" x2="10" y2="90" stroke="url(#thesisCandleGrad)" stroke-width="2"></line>
          <rect x="4" y="42" width="12" height="34" fill="url(#thesisCandleGrad)"></rect>
          <line x1="45" y1="10" x2="45" y2="70" stroke="url(#thesisCandleGrad)" stroke-width="2"></line>
          <rect x="39" y="20" width="12" height="30" fill="url(#thesisCandleGrad)"></rect>
          <line x1="80" y1="-10" x2="80" y2="50" stroke="url(#thesisCandleGrad)" stroke-width="2"></line>
          <rect x="74" y="0" width="12" height="40" fill="url(#thesisCandleGrad)"></rect>
          <line x1="115" y1="-45" x2="115" y2="20" stroke="url(#thesisCandleGrad)" stroke-width="2"></line>
          <rect x="109" y="-35" width="12" height="45" fill="url(#thesisCandleGrad)"></rect>
          <path d="M4,65 L45,35 L80,15 L115,-25" stroke="#E8112D" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.55"></path>
        </g>
      </svg>
      <div class="thesis-mask"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="thesis-text">
      <div class="section-tag">02 &mdash; Thesis</div>
      <h2>Kami percaya <span>kesabaran</span> adalah aset yang paling jarang dimiliki di pasar.</h2>
      <p>
        Bukan soal seberapa cepat modal bertumbuh, tapi seberapa lama ia bisa bertahan lewat
        siklus pasar yang berbeda-beda.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Capital Wawan dibangun di atas satu prinsip sederhana:</strong> uang bekerja
        paling baik ketika dikelola dengan data, bukan emosi. Kami memandang saham domestik dan
        aset kripto bukan sebagai instrumen spekulasi jangka pendek, melainkan sebagai kelas
        aset yang layak dipelajari secara mendalam, dipegang dengan keyakinan, dan dievaluasi
        ulang secara berkala.
      </p>
      <p>
        Fokus kami ada pada perusahaan dan protokol dengan fundamental yang jelas &mdash; baik
        itu emiten dengan model bisnis yang bisa dipertanggungjawabkan, atau jaringan blockchain
        dengan adopsi nyata. Kami tidak mengejar tren, kami mengevaluasi keduanya dengan standar
        yang sama ketatnya.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .thesis-masked {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 640px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: linear-gradient(245deg, #1c0508 0%, #0a0a0b 55%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .thesis-grid {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(420px, 760px);
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 640px;
    padding-right: max(32px, calc((100vw - 1180px) / 2));
  }

  .thesis-visual {
    position: relative;
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .thesis-photo {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 500px 700px at 30% 20%, rgba(232, 17, 45, 0.22), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(340deg, #2a0a0f 0%, #0a0a0b 65%);
  }

  .thesis-photo::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0 1px, transparent 1px 64px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0 1px, transparent 1px 64px);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .thesis-svg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .thesis-mask {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(270deg, var(--bg) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 11, 0.75) 22%, transparent 55%);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .thesis-text {
    grid-column: 2;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    padding: 100px 32px 100px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .thesis-text .section-tag {
    color: var(--red);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .thesis-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 40px);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .thesis-text h2 span {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .thesis-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--copy);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .thesis-text p strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .thesis-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
      padding-right: 0;
    }
    .thesis-visual {
      grid-column: 1;
      height: 280px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .thesis-text {
      grid-column: 1;
      padding: 40px 20px 60px;
    }
    .thesis-mask {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, var(--bg) 90%);
    }
  }
</style>
